  "title": "Kitchen Assistant @ Tuas | Rotating shift |Up $2.8K",
  "description": "<p>Description</p>\n<p><strong>📍 Location: </strong>Jalan Ahmad Ibrahim</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our Central Kitchen is growing, and we’re hiring 20<strong> dedicated Operations Crew members</strong> to support large-scale food production. If you're hardworking, shift-flexible, and ready to be part of a high-volume kitchen team — we want to hear from you!</p>\n<h3>🍽️ <strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist with daily central kitchen operations</li>\n  <li>Prepare raw materials for cooking</li>\n  <li>Portion and pack cooked meals (bentos, staff meals, catering orders)</li>\n  <li>Maintain kitchen hygiene: cleaning, washing, and sanitisation duties</li>\n  <li>Support timely execution of daily meals and festive specials</li>\n  <li>Work as a team to uphold service and product standards</li>\n  <li>Perform other ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>💼 <strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min 1 year experience in F&amp;B or food manufacturing environment</li>\n  <li>WSQ <strong>Food Safety Course Level 1</strong> preferred</li>\n  <li>Able to handle long standing hours and a fast-paced setting</li>\n  <li><strong>Open to shift work</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>⏰ <strong>Working Hours &amp; Shifts</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Per day work shift 9.5 hours</strong> (8.75 hrs work + 45 mins break)</li>\n  <li><strong>5 days/week</strong> (Rostered, Monday to Sunday)</li>\n  <li>Shift Allowances (per day): Morning +$8 per day, Noon +$8 per day, Night + $15 per day</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>💰 <strong>Salary</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Base Salary:</strong> $2,000 – $2,500 (based on experience) + Allowances</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ready to contribute to a meaningful role in a kitchen?<br>\n📧 <strong>Email:</strong> deborah@crew.sg<br>\n(Please include your resume and availability)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ho Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)</strong><br>\nHRnet Ventures Pte Ltd | EA Licence: <strong>24C2435</strong></p>",
